Introduction

INI is an eleven-member japanese boy group under LAPONE Entertainment. They were formed from the winners of Produce 101 Japan Season 2. They debuted on November 3, 2021, with their mini album "A".

The group name “INI” represents the connection between the members (I) and the fans (I) through Network (N). Their fandom name is MINI (Memory and INI), which means that INI and their fans are going to make memories together.
